        "Title": "Rescuing Ringo - I",
        "Location": "LOCATION_BANGKOK",
        "PublicId": "108704426106",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/Bangkok/_scene_tiger.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository a435d5bd-1b8c-4f2f-ab6b-a322ddb6c3cb).Image",
        "Description": "47!\r\rOne of our agents by the name of Snail has recently lost his pet rabbit! He originally thought he just escaped from his cage somehow, but we realized that instead, Providence is using Ringo as leverage, and says they will keep him forever unless we give them an important document regarding a classified mission that happened a few years back in Romania. We have traced down a few of the possible Ringo Robbers, and we begin in Bangkok. \r\rEliminate them now, 47. Good luck.",
